<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 16:08:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“如果以色列要这样对待人民，那么他们制定回归法还有什么意义呢？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/whats-the-point-of-having-a-law-of-return-if-theyre-going-to-treat-people-like-this/0000018e-2d0d-dbcf-abee-3ddd4d2d0000</link><description>在发给每个前往以色列回返的人的表格上诚实地回答一个人的心理健康史，有时会让移民走上侵入性询问和长期拖延的道路。一名女性的案例终于可以解决这个问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 15:54:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/whats-the-point-of-having-a-law-of-return-if-theyre-going-to-treat-people-like-this/0000018e-2d0d-dbcf-abee-3ddd4d2d0000</guid></item><item><title>非政府组织起诉丹麦向以色列出售武器，并援引加沙“潜在的种族灭绝”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-12/ty-article/ngos-sue-denmark-over-arms-sales-to-israel-cite-potential-genocide-in-gaza/0000018e-3316-d606-a5ff-7fb760a30000</link><description>参与诉讼的组织之一的秘书长表示，政客们没有采取行动阻止“加沙潜在的种族灭绝”。上个月，荷兰法院下令荷兰禁止向以色列出口所有 F-35 战斗机零部件</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 15:17:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-12/ty-article/ngos-sue-denmark-over-arms-sales-to-israel-cite-potential-genocide-in-gaza/0000018e-3316-d606-a5ff-7fb760a30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军袭击黎巴嫩深处的真主党据点； 100枚火箭弹袭击以色列北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/idf-strikes-hezbollah-stronghold-deep-in-lebanon-100-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel/0000018e-3263-df45-afaf-3f7775df0000</link><description>以色列战机袭击了距以色列北部边境一百多公里的巴勒贝克的真主党目标后，真主党向戈兰高地发射了战争中最大规模的火箭弹之一</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 14:49:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/idf-strikes-hezbollah-stronghold-deep-in-lebanon-100-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel/0000018e-3263-df45-afaf-3f7775df0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列的新民族主义犹太教不关心加沙的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-israels-new-nationalistic-judaism-doesnt-care-about-the-hostages-in-gaza/0000018e-32d0-d5ad-addf-7ed15b390000</link><description>对于以色列不断崛起的沙文主义、救世主宗教右翼来说，加沙战争是为了恢复自豪感和投射权力。哈马斯扣押的绝望人质与他们的叙述不符</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 14:42:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-israels-new-nationalistic-judaism-doesnt-care-about-the-hostages-in-gaza/0000018e-32d0-d5ad-addf-7ed15b390000</guid></item><item><title>征服巴勒斯坦人的计划继续进行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/the-plan-to-subjugate-the-palestinians-goes-ahead/0000018e-32ae-d606-a5ff-7fbf31c80000</link><description>即使是那些嘲笑财政部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇的人也参与或通过沉默大声支持政府对世界各地的巴勒斯坦人使用压倒性的武力</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 13:33:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/the-plan-to-subjugate-the-palestinians-goes-ahead/0000018e-32ae-d606-a5ff-7fbf31c80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队宣布一名士兵死亡，该士兵被认为自 10 月 7 日起被绑架，尸体被扣留在加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/israeli-army-announces-death-of-soldier-thought-kidnapped-since-oct-7-body-held-in-gaza/0000018e-32bc-d606-a5ff-7fbf024a0000</link><description>19岁的陈拥有美国和以色列双重国籍，曾在陆军装甲兵第75营服役</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 13:26:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/israeli-army-announces-death-of-soldier-thought-kidnapped-since-oct-7-body-held-in-gaza/0000018e-32bc-d606-a5ff-7fbf024a0000</guid></item><item><title>人质的贝都因以色列亲属在联合国与巴勒斯坦特使对峙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/bedouin-israeli-relative-of-hostages-confronts-palestinian-envoy-at-united-nations/0000018e-327d-d5ad-addf-7e7dacf00000</link><description>10 月 7 日，阿里·阿尔齐亚达纳 (Ali Alziadana) 的四名亲属在加沙被绑架，之后他陪同以色列代表团前往联合国。 ■ “他们在没有达成协议的情况下遣返了泰国工人，而像我和你这样的穆斯林则被留在隧道里挨饿，”他告诉巴勒斯坦驻联合国大使</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 12:41:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/bedouin-israeli-relative-of-hostages-confronts-palestinian-envoy-at-united-nations/0000018e-327d-d5ad-addf-7e7dacf00000</guid></item><item><title>寻找失踪的 9 岁以色列女孩：“可怕的人在这里徘徊”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-where-a-9-year-old-israeli-girl-went-missing-scary-people-hang-around-there/0000018e-2d39-dc45-a7ef-6dfd0fd70000</link><description>海马诺特卡绍在哪里？ 9岁的埃塞俄比亚以色列女孩失踪两周后，她的家人开始绝望。每个人似乎都同意的一件事是吸收中心的较低楼层是一个危险的地方</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 12:28:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-where-a-9-year-old-israeli-girl-went-missing-scary-people-hang-around-there/0000018e-2d39-dc45-a7ef-6dfd0fd70000</guid></item><item><title>如何打招呼以及何时不应该打电话：有关斋月的 8 件事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/8-things-to-know-about-ramadan-2022-greetings-fasting-meaning-israel/0000017f-db6b-df9c-a17f-ff7b8f4b0000</link><description>以色列 2024 年斋月：问候、斋戒和穆斯林节日意义的简单指南</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 12:18:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/8-things-to-know-about-ramadan-2022-greetings-fasting-meaning-israel/0000017f-db6b-df9c-a17f-ff7b8f4b0000</guid></item><item><title>人质陷入以色列对胜利形象的需要和哈马斯的要求之间</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/the-hostages-are-stuck-between-israels-victory-image-and-hamas-demands/0000018e-3208-de0a-a5de-3bc9f5bb0000</link><description>以色列摩萨德和哈马斯领导人上周就谈判进展交换了声明。虽然摩萨德的言论表明哈马斯对达成协议“不感兴趣”，但哈马斯对达成协议的愿景似乎比以色列更清晰</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 11:32:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/the-hostages-are-stuck-between-israels-victory-image-and-hamas-demands/0000018e-3208-de0a-a5de-3bc9f5bb0000</guid></item><item><title>国家网络局警告国家档案馆：以色列的数字历史可能被删除</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/national-cyber-directorate-warns-israels-digital-history-could-be-erased/0000018e-31b6-d12e-ad8e-fdbed75a0000</link><description>以色列国家档案馆网站自去年11月遭到亲巴勒斯坦黑客攻击以来，搜索功能已被禁用。国家网络管理局警告说，档案中的关键材料极易遭受不可逆转的损害</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 10:39:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/national-cyber-directorate-warns-israels-digital-history-could-be-erased/0000018e-31b6-d12e-ad8e-fdbed75a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列通过法律允许恐怖主义受害者起诉巴勒斯坦权力机构要求赔偿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-passes-law-allowing-terror-victims-to-sue-palestinian-authority-for-compensation/0000018e-2f39-d920-adce-2fbddfbc0000</link><description>这项法律是在安全内阁决定防止巴勒斯坦权力机构崩溃三周后出台的，该法律将允许永久残疾的恐怖受害者和在恐怖袭击中丧生的人的亲属起诉巴勒斯坦权力机构要求赔偿</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 06:26:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-passes-law-allowing-terror-victims-to-sue-palestinian-authority-for-compensation/0000018e-2f39-d920-adce-2fbddfbc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军宣布一名疑似于 10 月 7 日被绑架的士兵死亡，尸体在加沙扣留</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article-live/yemen-govt-u-s-british-forces-strike-houthi-targets-killing-11/0000018e-30ce-d12e-ad8e-fcde25cb0000</link><description>以色列军队说中士。 10 月 7 日，伊泰·陈 (Itay Chen) 在哈马斯袭击中丧生，他的尸体被绑架到加沙 ■ 向以色列北部和戈兰高地发射 100 枚火箭弹后，以色列空军深入黎巴嫩境内，瞄准真主党地点</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 04:15:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article-live/yemen-govt-u-s-british-forces-strike-houthi-targets-killing-11/0000018e-30ce-d12e-ad8e-fcde25cb0000</guid></item><item><title>数百人在伯克利游行，要求犹太学生的安全和言论自由</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-march-at-berkeley-demanding-safety-free-speech-for-jewish-students/0000018e-3016-d2d7-a1fe-b337c3640000</link><description>这次游行的起因是两周前爆发的一场骚乱，当时一名以色列退伍军人受邀在校园演讲，200 名反以色列抗议者冲进了活动现场</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 02:07:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-march-at-berkeley-demanding-safety-free-speech-for-jewish-students/0000018e-3016-d2d7-a1fe-b337c3640000</guid></item><item><title>斋月第一周，圣殿山局势紧张</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/tensions-run-high-on-the-temple-mount-during-first-week-of-ramadan/0000018e-2f25-d86c-abae-3f6dd97a0000</link><description>一位高级安全官员表示，以色列国家安全部长本-格维尔渴望看到一场重大冲突。 “本-格维尔对此事没有发言权，也不会干预任何运营决策。另一位官员表示：“我们没有兴趣让事态升温。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 23:44:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/tensions-run-high-on-the-temple-mount-during-first-week-of-ramadan/0000018e-2f25-d86c-abae-3f6dd97a0000</guid></item><item><title>联合国特使彭定康表示，她亲眼目睹了哈马斯实施的“难以形容的”性暴力行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/un-envoy-patten-says-she-saw-unspeakable-sexual-violence-perpetrated-by-hamas/0000018e-2fc8-dcb3-a58f-efcd7d340000</link><description>联合国安理会10月7日在纽约召​​开特别听证会，介绍联合国关于哈马斯性暴力行为报告的调查结果</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 23:26:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/un-envoy-patten-says-she-saw-unspeakable-sexual-violence-perpetrated-by-hamas/0000018e-2fc8-dcb3-a58f-efcd7d340000</guid></item><item><title>因拆除加沙大学而受到谴责的以色列国防军军官可能成为内塔尼亚胡的军事秘书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-officer-reprimanded-for-gaza-university-demolition-may-become-top-netanyahu-aid/0000018e-2f1a-d920-adce-2f9ee9f90000</link><description>双桅船。 10 月 7 日，指挥官巴拉克·希拉姆 (Barak Hiram) 下令炮击贝埃里基布兹 (Kibbutz Be&amp;#39;eri) 的一座房屋，里面有以色列人质，所有人都死了。他最近接受了内塔尼亚胡的军事秘书一职采访</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 20:42:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-officer-reprimanded-for-gaza-university-demolition-may-become-top-netanyahu-aid/0000018e-2f1a-d920-adce-2f9ee9f90000</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰苦难的奥斯卡奖，加沙的黑暗预兆</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-11/ty-article/.highlight/an-oscar-for-ukraines-suffering-a-dark-portent-for-gaza/0000018e-2ed8-d468-a9ff-2ef968480000</link><description>我们在这里，看着乌克兰首位奥斯卡奖得主恳求世界回忆乌克兰在战争爆发两年多后所遭受的恐怖苦难。两年后，以色列在加沙的战争将会走向何方？</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 20:10:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-11/ty-article/.highlight/an-oscar-for-ukraines-suffering-a-dark-portent-for-gaza/0000018e-2ed8-d468-a9ff-2ef968480000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方24小时内调查以色列多个城市的三起疑似凶杀案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-investigate-three-suspected-homicides-in-24-hour-period-in-multiple-cities/0000018e-2eae-dcb3-a58f-efaf01280000</link><description>一个妇女权利组织就一名 48 岁妇女的死亡事件表示，“在战争背景下，妇女继续被谋杀并在家中遭受暴力”</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 19:19:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-investigate-three-suspected-homicides-in-24-hour-period-in-multiple-cities/0000018e-2eae-dcb3-a58f-efaf01280000</guid></item><item><title>文学杂志撤回以色列作家关于共存的文章</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/literary-magazine-retracts-israeli-writers-essay-on-coexistence/0000018e-2ea8-d12e-ad8e-eeba04330000</link><description>《格尔尼卡》杂志撤稿之前，多名工作人员因一位以色列作家发表的文章公开辞职，该文章讲述了她在 10 月 7 日之后致力于共存并试图与巴勒斯坦人寻求相互理解的情况</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 18:38:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/literary-magazine-retracts-israeli-writers-essay-on-coexistence/0000018e-2ea8-d12e-ad8e-eeba04330000</guid></item></channel></rss>